Features included:
- Viewer/editor roles via local sign-in
- Editors can create and edit pages
- Every edit creates a revision
- Revision history, revision viewing, and restore support
- Editor-only pages hidden/blocked from viewers
- SQLite database auto-created as `wiki.sqlite3`
