The app includes SQLite persistence, setup-first-manager flow, bcrypt password hashing, session auth, manager vs sales access control, contacts/deals CRUD, pipeline board stage moves, CSRF protection, parameterized SQL, validation, Helmet security headers, secure cookie configuration, and generic client-facing errors.

